app name Her Safety

Features different interfaces for police station and users.

Users app has live location tracking, direct updates to police station.
Ability to share loction to trusted contacts.
Simlple and easy UI with a Panic button.


Police app shows list of users in the zone of the concerned police station.
Ploice can see the live location of user.

HERE technologies features used
Routing API,
Reverse Geo Coding,
Custom Location using POI,


List of Activities in User App:-
1. Login Activity
2. Nearest Police Station Activity
3. Send Location to police

List of Activities in Police App:-
1. Check the list of users that need help
2. Get the direction for their location Activity

How to set up App- 
The app cannot be hosted to server, it can just be installed on phone.
